title: Ella Henderson Covers Taylor Swift's 'Wildest Dreams' With Kygo - newsR
text: Ella Henderson keeps dry underneath an umbrella while arriving at BBC Radio in London, England on Tuesday afternoon (October 6). The 19-year-old singer met up with Kygo at the studios for the Live Lounge, where they performed a cover of Taylor Swift ‘s “Wildest Dreams”.
